name: Snatchers
overview: High schooler Sara wakes up pregnant…with an alien baby. Now she’ll have to team up with her ex-best friend Hayley to fight the extraterrestrial threat and save the world.

episodes.name: One
episodes.overview: Sara is killing it at the popularity game, but when her ex Skyler threatens her reputation, Sara goes to big lengths to keep her status...not knowing how big the consequences will be.

episodes.name: Two
episodes.overview: Things go from weird to super freaky when Sara wakes up nine-months pregnant overnight. She turns to her nerdy ex-bestie Hayley to find a quiet solution to her predicament.

episodes.name: Three
episodes.overview: A trip to the clinic goes totally horrific when Sara finds that her problem isn't just gynecological...it's extraterrestrial.

episodes.name: Four
episodes.overview: The girls attempt to escape their alien pursuer...but a whole new dilemma demands a different approach.

episodes.name: Five
episodes.overview: Sara tries to keep her predicament under wraps, which is easier said than done when her mom makes an unexpected appearance.

episodes.name: Six
episodes.overview: The girls visit an old friend on the outskirts of town in the hopes of solving their alien problem for good, but it seems they've got another stalker on their trail…

episodes.name: Seven
episodes.overview: Sara's night goes full-on dysfunctional when she's brought down to the police station and confronted by her apoplectic mom.

episodes.name: Eight
episodes.overview: Things come to a head when the alien threat catches up to the girls. It's up to Sara to finish the job before it's too late, but even an entire police force might not be enough to stop this monstrous force.
